{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52049, "create_time": 1647406861, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "政策研究肯定需要一个能够量化的东西…和一个大家都能接受的死亡率相比，不是没有道理的，但如果光看死亡率也是不科学的", "timestamp": 1647406861}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52064, "create_time": 1647407402, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "现在用死亡率、病死率这种单一的指标有点过时了。有个新概念叫做疾病负担（burden of disease）：疾病、 伤残和过早死亡对整个社会经济及健康的压力。", "timestamp": 1647407402}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52065, "create_time": 1647407519, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "（下面开始加私货）\n年轻人感染新冠，死亡率比老年人低得多。但同一场车祸，年轻人和老年人的死亡率差不多。所以，如果讨论“过早死亡”（premature death），车祸可能比新冠更厉害。\n而且疾病负担并没有考虑动辄封控对人心理健康的影响。", "timestamp": 1647407519}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52067, "create_time": 1647407856, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 这里没有道德判断吗，\n新冠如果防控就可以少死，而车祸不可避免。\n如果只从指标考虑，不如说按量屠杀老年人是个好政策", "timestamp": 1647407856}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52069, "create_time": 1647407932, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Carol: 六十岁以上老人直接送进屠宰场，为国民经济减负", "timestamp": 1647407932}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52086, "create_time": 1647409285, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 如果按你说额这样做，老年人的死亡率会急剧上升，60岁以上的死亡率达到100%，人均预期寿命会变成小于60岁，指标当然会变差很多，你在想什么？？其次，车祸当然是可以避免的，公交车停运、出租车停运、禁止私家车上路就可以了，很多城市疫情防控的时候就是这样做的。", "timestamp": 1647409285}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52092, "create_time": 1647409877, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "没有 因为新冠是病毒的错而车祸大多是人祸", "timestamp": 1647409877}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 52258, "create_time": 1647423301, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "不能，因为车祸不会传染。", "timestamp": 1647423301}], "create_time": 1647406449, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1647423301, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 8, "pid": 18998, "poll": null, "reply": 8, "text": "新冠和车祸是否具有可比性？", "timestamp": 1647406449}}